{
  "stem": "6526.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was the men's camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was the women's camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a hospital camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a gypsy camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On one side with us was the gypsies, and on the other side were the women, the women's camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the women's camp was a little further out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We could shout to them, but we couldn't see them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the gypsy camp was next to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Beyond the gypsy camp was the hospital camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But people used to be sick or they used to take the-- who wanted to heal them, whether they were good, just maybe minor things.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we-- they took us to work in the hospital camp to straighten the streets out, the road, because there was a lot of clay.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as soon as you went in to step into clay, and you tried to get out, you went in with the other foot, and it would straighten out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Next to the hospital camp was the crematoria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we've seen what was going on, all this time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it came to us to see, well, if a transport comes, I'm going to push myself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He says, only far away from the crematory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we didn't realize that when they want you, they're just going to bring you back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And a matter of fact, they did, because when we went, Landsman from my own town, which I met him in, in, in-- he came over from Majdanek, but I didn't seem him in Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He came with me together to Birkenau, .",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Went to that camp, to a new camp called Lagischa.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a camp to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was a concentration camp under guard.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
